00:43:19,120 --> 00:43:23,660
You little!!

614
00:43:43,650 --> 00:43:45,320
Excuse me.

615
00:43:46,210 --> 00:43:47,840
Thank you.

616
00:43:52,940 --> 00:43:54,970
Mr. Jin Moo Hak.

617
00:43:58,490 --> 00:44:00,120
What is it?

618
00:44:02,160 --> 00:44:04,930
