623
00:44:18,420 --> 00:44:22,060
not arrogantly request for the other to go meet them.

624
00:44:22,060 --> 00:44:24,340
That's what I said.

625
00:44:26,100 --> 00:44:29,010
I was trying to be considerate of your time.

626
00:44:29,010 --> 00:44:31,490
I'll apologize if you were offended.

627
00:44:31,490 --> 00:44:33,180
"Considerate"?

628
00:44:33,940 --> 00:44:38,150
If you say so. Anyways, do you have something to discuss with me?

629
00:44:38,150 --> 00:44:41,570
I heard that my Dali owes you a debt.

630
00:44:41,570 --> 00:44:44,200
I should've taken care of it sooner.

631
00:44:44,200 --> 00:44:47,040
But the two of us had some personal issues,

632
00:44:47,040 --> 00:44:49,530
so it's been delayed until now.

633
00:44:49,530 --> 00:44:51,120
The two of them?

634
00:44:51,120 --> 00:44:53,160
Personal?

635
00:44:54,370 --> 00:44:56,060
So, what?

636
00:44:57,580 --> 00:44:59,450
"So, what"?

637
00:45:02,980 --> 00:45:08,250
So... I'll pay back the debt that Cheongsong owes you.

638
00:45:12,950 --> 00:45:16,400
What gives you the right? Huh?

639
00:45:16,400 --> 00:45:19,510
What gives you the right to butt into what's between me and Kim Dali.

640
00:45:19,510 --> 00:45:24,330
I can no longer stand back and watch her being surrounded and harassed by people like you.

641
00:45:24,330 --> 00:45:27,550
Men with tattoos lying down on the art museum's floor,

642
00:45:27,550 --> 00:45:32,800
ruining artworks, and chasing her around while watching her every move.

643
00:45:32,800 --> 00:45:36,590
She's grown up her entire life surrounded by only books and artworks.

644
00:45:36,590 --> 00:45:39,320
She's different from you.

645
00:45:39,320 --> 00:45:42,370
She may not show it because she has a strong sense of duty and responsibility.

646
00:45:42,370 --> 00:45:43,930
But can't you see...

647
00:45:43,930 --> 00:45:47,540
