648
00:45:47,540 --> 00:45:49,590
Did Kim Dali say that?

649
00:45:49,590 --> 00:45:52,120
That she's struggling because of me?

650
00:45:54,840 --> 00:45:58,430
That's not what she said to me.

651
00:45:58,430 --> 00:46:01,770
Also, Kim Dali...

652
00:46:01,770 --> 00:46:05,340
She's not as weak as you think.

653
00:46:06,330 --> 00:46:09,760
Can't you see? That she's doing well?

654
00:46:19,980 --> 00:46:23,070
