659
00:46:45,360 --> 00:46:47,580
Yes, hello?

660
00:46:47,580 --> 00:46:51,550
All right, I got it. I'm going now.

661
00:46:53,770 --> 00:46:56,320
I'm a little busy.

662
00:46:56,320 --> 00:46:58,430
I thought you liked money.

663
00:47:01,680 --> 00:47:04,440
All you need is your money, isn't that right?

664
00:47:06,030 --> 00:47:09,450
You're right, I'm obsessed with money.

665
00:47:09,450 --> 00:47:14,300
But I don't take free money. It makes me sick.

666
00:47:24,080 --> 00:47:29,400
This is Hong Ja Yeong's third piece from her "The Living and The Dead" series.

667
00:47:29,400 --> 00:47:33,410
As you can see, the piece is made of waste that only the living can generate,

668
00:47:33,410 --> 00:47:36,150
that is, trash.

