674
00:48:00,850 --> 00:48:06,690
Her mother requested that her daughter, who was preparing for an important exhibition, should not be bothered.

675
00:48:06,690 --> 00:48:11,280
During that one month, to the artist, was her mother, "the living"

676
00:48:11,280 --> 00:48:13,590
